[SDG-FETCH]: run sdgfetch to display system info with your selected logo and preset
[SDG-FETCH]: sdgfetch config lets you pick logos and presets interactively with live previews
[SDG-FETCH]: add custom logos by placing ASCII art files in ~/.local/fetch/logos/<yourname>/
[SDG-FETCH]: sdgfetch convert <image> converts PNG/JPG to ASCII art for use as a logo
[SDG-FETCH]: sdgfetch <logoname> shows the specified logo via grep matching
